<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104exx1665702784515.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exx1665702784515.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exx1665702784515.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"exx1665702784515\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> appends the instance name of the static\n    server page to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute that it generates for the\n      <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">x-id</span> placeholder attribute.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144194e1_d144195e1_d144196e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> |\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exx1665702784515__section_edj_hkn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d326659e74\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"exx1665702784515__table_d17483e1_d17484e1_d17485e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[WEB]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Alias:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">[SETTINGS]</code>\n                  \\<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME</span> (Deprecated) </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exx1665702784515__section_s1z_kkn_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d326659e136\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144203e1_d144204e1_d144205e1\">By default, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> does not\n        generate <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attributes for the XHTML controls that represent Uniface fields\n        in static server pages. It is possible to change this behavior globally by setting\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>, or locally by adding\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">x-id=\"1\"</code> to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst\n          type=\"<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldType</var>\"&gt;</code>. This causes <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> to\n        generate an <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attribute that has the same value as the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">name</code> attribute.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144206e1_d144207e1_d144208e1\">You can append the instance name of the USP to the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME</span>=<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.\n        The resulting <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> would have the format:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144209e1_d144210e1_d144211e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">id=\"</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">E</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SequenceNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModelName</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>}{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144212e1_d144213e1_d144214e1\">This is also the format used for value of the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code> attribute, if <code class=\"ph codeph\"> x-for=\"1\"</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144215e1_d144216e1_d144217e1\">For more information, see the \"x-id\" topic.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exx1665702784515__p_d144218e1_d144219e1_d144220e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME</span> is ignored if\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> does not generate <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attributes in this\n        fashion.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ucm1665702784446.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT</a><p>Determines the default value of the x-id placeholder attribute for fields in static server pages.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/agi1665702784377.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT</a><p>Determines the default value of the x-for placeholder attribute for associated labels in static server pages.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a><p>XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527388\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527388\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME Determines whether webgen appends the instance name of the static server page to the id attribute that it generates for the x-id placeholder attribute. $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME { = } 1 | 0 Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [WEB] Default value: 0 Alias: [SETTINGS] \\ $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME (Deprecated) Description By default, webgen does not generate id attributes for the XHTML controls that represent Uniface fields in static server pages. It is possible to change this behavior globally by setting $WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT to true , or locally by adding x-id=\"1\" to the <x-subst type=\" FieldType \"> . This causes webgen to generate an id attribute that has the same value as the name attribute. You can append the instance name of the USP to the id by setting $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME = 1 . The resulting id would have the format: id=\" { E SequenceNumber . } FieldName . EntityName . ModelName { . OccurrenceNumber }{ . InstanceName } \" This is also the format used for value of the for attribute, if x-for=\"1\" . For more information, see the \"x-id\" topic. $WEBGEN_X_ID_INSNAME is ignored if webgen does not generate id attributes in this fashion. Related Links $WEBGEN_X_ID_DEFAULT Determines the default value of the x-id placeholder attribute for fields in static server pages. $WEBGEN_X_FOR_DEFAULT Determines the default value of the x-for placeholder attribute for associated labels in static server pages. <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}